sentences.english: And for those who find their fears were justified, many head straight to divorce court.

sentences.english: He was troubled by religious doubt.

sentences.english: China will dominate them or not after rising made them apprehensions.

sentences.english: As soon as passed through the apprehensions, the matter is that serious.

sentences.english: His mind boggles at the king's arrogance.
